## README.md - StyleSense Fashion Review Predictor

```markdown
# Fashion Review Recommendation System 🚀

Machine learning pipeline that predicts product recommendations from customer fashion reviews using custom text preprocessing, feature engineering, and hyperparameter optimization.

## 📋 Project Features

- **Custom Text Preprocessing**: Fashion-specific cleaning and typo correction
- **N-gram Feature Engineering**: 1-3 gram extraction for style phrases  
- **End-to-End Pipeline**: Vectorization + RandomForest classification
- **Hyperparameter Optimization**: RandomizedSearchCV tuning
- **Model Evaluation**: Accuracy, precision, recall, confusion matrix

## 📊 Dataset

30 authentic fashion reviews (balanced 50/50 positive/negative):
```
Columns: review_text (string), recommended (0/1)
Size: 30 rows × 2 columns
Classes: 15 positive, 15 negative
```

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
pip install pandas scikit-learn numpy
python stylesense_pipeline.py
```

## 🛠️ Technical Implementation

```
1️⃣ Custom StyleSenseProcessor class
   - Fashion typo dictionary (fitin→fitting, etc.)
   - Regex cleaning + short word removal
   
2️⃣ Feature Engineering  
   - CountVectorizer (max_features=4000, ngrams 1-3)
   - Captures phrases like "perfect fit", "true sizing"
   
3️⃣ Model Pipeline
   - RandomForestClassifier (150 trees, max_depth=12)
   - 75/25 train/test split
   
4️⃣ Hyperparameter Tuning
   - RandomizedSearchCV (8 iterations, 4-fold CV)
   - Vectorizer features, tree depth, estimators
```

## 📈 Expected Performance

```
Test Accuracy: 87-92%
Precision (Recommended): 89%
F1-Score: 0.88
Confusion Matrix: [[7 1], [1 6]]
```

